section.name: Course Conclusion
section.summary:
This unit wraps up the course by guiding you through creating a SMART goal action plan using the action steps you identified.

By the end of this unit, you will be able to articulate a SMART goal and develop a plan based on the action steps you identified in previous units.

After you have completed the activities in this section, please be sure to complete the course evaluation and save or print your course certificate.
